data.description: This exceptional 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom all-brick ranch home not only offers a spacious family room with vaulted ceilings, a charming brick fireplace with an electric insert, and a grand dining room, but also features a magnificent double-tiered deck that elevates your outdoor entertaining experience. The basement features a full bathroom and spacious closet, providing ample storage space for your entertaining essentials and offering exciting potential for transformation into an in-law suite, making it easy to accommodate extended family members or overnight guests. Recent upgrades include new indoor water lines, a state-of-the-art gas tankless water heater, upgraded bathrooms, and luxurious new vinyl plank flooring, ensuring your home is stylish and equipped with modern comfort. Gather with loved ones in a dining room that comfortably seats 12, setting the stage for memorable meals and celebrations. Step into your private outdoor haven with a spacious fenced backyard, complete with a two level deck and a sizable shed, offering endless opportunities for outdoor enjoyment. The two-car garage not only provides a shelter for your vehicles but also offers ample extra storage space. Join a welcoming community where camaraderie thrives, creating not just a home but a network of supportive friends. Embrace the freedom of no HOA restrictions, allowing you to personalize your living space and outdoor entertaining areas how you see fit. Families will appreciate the convenience of a school bus stop right across the street, ensuring a seamless start to the school day for their children. Don't miss this exceptional investment opportunity that promises lucrative returns. Whether you're venturing into Airbnb hosting or seeking a reliable long-term income stream, this residence offers endless possibilities. Schedule a showing today and embark on a new chapter of comfort and style! ****   Need to Sell? Buy This Home and We will Buy Yours with Quickbuy! ***   *** Interest Rates Woes? 2/1 Interest Rate Buydown Available with Preferred Lender!! *** Seller willing to buy down buyer’s mortgage rate by 2% their first year and by 1% their second year with a full priced offer.
